---
<% 
const isMetavuln = item.problem && item.chain
const advisory = isMetavuln ? item.problem : item
const chain = isMetavuln ? item.chain : []
%>
### <%- advisory.title %>

| 字段 | 详情 |
| --- | --- |
| **漏洞来源包** | `<%- advisory.name %>` |
<%if(isMetavuln){%>| **依赖链条** | `<%- chain.join(' → ') %>` |<%}%>| **受影响版本** | `<%- advisory.range %>` |
| **CWE 分类** | <%- advisory.cwe.join('、') %> |
| **CVSS 评分** | <%- advisory.cvss.score %> |
| **CVSS 向量** | `<%- advisory.cvss.vectorString %>` |
| **详情链接** | [<%- advisory.url %>](<%- advisory.url %>) |